snippet.title: Disc Space - Online Ultimate Frisbee Game
snippet.description:
Disc Space is a multiplayer Ultimate Frisbee game with up to 10 players online. 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1452830/
https://discspace.itch.io/play

Play with your friends or find new ones. 
Unlimited fun is guaranteed.

Features:
- Play 3v3, 4v4, 5v5 Ultimate Frisbee game
- Play with your friends or find new ones (you could also play with or against 'Computer AI')
- Select specialization to match your play style: Handler, Cutter, Cannon, Newbie or D-Machine
